For your information, JP, the newcomers didn't attack the Cybertronian Fire, 
they attacked the Ark. The Cybertronian Fire is still fully functional, 
except for the engines.

::Kluster::

Kluster nods, the info that Phobia had given his sinking in. "Destroy this 
planet?" Kluster frowns, "They would first rescue the predacons. This is 
serious," he looks at Phobia, "The Council wouldn't do that, it would destroy 
most of their army."

He stands up, going to a comp console. "Are you suggesting we attack the Iron 
Fist?"
